data.title: President Vladimir Putin met at the Kremlin with President of the Cooperative Republic of Guyana Bharrat Jagdeo • President of Russia
data.text:
Opening the meeting, Mr Putin expressed satisfaction with the development of bilateral cooperation between Russian and Guyanese business organisations and the two countries’ fruitful relations in culture and education.

Mr Putin congratulated Mr Jagdeo on his recent birthday and on his re-election to the post of president.
